dct_description_sm: Map shows: administrative divisions, land use, subways, places of worship, places of interest to tourists. Panel title Includes indexes, text, abbreviations, advertisements, colored images, and tourist information. On top of panel title "2013" Verso maps show metro, railway, cable cars routes. Index of Lignes etusa and Lignes téléphérique
